pesquisaveis.valor: (select coalesce(pfa.nome, pja.razaosocial)                   from ADQUIRENTESSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE aitbi                            inner join CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE CALC                                       on aitbi.CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = CALC.id                            left join pessoafisica pfa on aitbi.ADQUIRENTE_ID = pfa.id                            left join pessoajuridica pja on aitbi.ADQUIRENTE_ID = pja.id                   where CALC.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID                     and CALC.id = (select c2.id                                    from CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE c2                                    where c2.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID                                    order by c2.ordemcalculo desc fetch first 1 rows only))

(select listagg(coalesce(pfa.CPF, pja.CNPJ), '; ')                       within group (order by coalesce(pfa.nome, pja.razaosocial) desc)        from ADQUIRENTESSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE aitbi                 inner join CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE CALC on aitbi.CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = CALC.id                 left join pessoafisica pfa on aitbi.ADQUIRENTE_ID = pfa.id                 left join pessoajuridica pja on aitbi.ADQUIRENTE_ID = pja.id        where CALC.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID          and CALC.id = (select c2.id                         from CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE c2                         where c2.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID                         order by c2.ordemcalculo desc fetch first 1 rows only))

(select listagg(lower(coalesce(pft.nome, pjt.razaosocial)), '; ')                       within group (order by coalesce(pft.nome, pjt.razaosocial) desc)        from TRANSMITENTESSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE titbi                 inner join CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE CALC on titbi.CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = CALC.id                 left join pessoafisica pft on titbi.TRANSMITENTE_ID = pft.id                 left join pessoajuridica pjt on titbi.TRANSMITENTE_ID = pjt.id        where CALC.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID          and CALC.id = (select c2.id                         from CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE c2                         where c2.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID                         order by c2.ordemcalculo desc fetch first 1 rows only))

(select listagg(coalesce(pft.CPF, pjt.CNPJ), '; ')                       within group (order by coalesce(pft.nome, pjt.razaosocial) desc)        from TRANSMITENTESSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE titbi                 inner join CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE CALC on titbi.CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = CALC.id                 left join pessoafisica pft on titbi.TRANSMITENTE_ID = pft.id                 left join pessoajuridica pjt on titbi.TRANSMITENTE_ID = pjt.id        where CALC.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID          and CALC.id = (select c2.id                         from CALCULOSOLICITACAOITBIONLINE c2                         where c2.SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE_ID = SIO.ID                         order by c2.ordemcalculo desc fetch first 1 rows only))

from:
FROM SOLICITACAOITBIONLINE SIO
INNER JOIN EXERCICIO EX ON EX.ID = SIO.EXERCICIO_ID
LEFT JOIN CADASTROIMOBILIARIO CI ON SIO.CADASTROIMOBILIARIO_ID = CI.ID
LEFT JOIN CADASTRORURAL CR ON SIO.CADASTRORURAL_ID = CR.ID
